descriptionHtml:
A High Elf saved file, a character i feel proud enough to upload it on the Nexus. Granted my character creation skills are not as good as some other people; but i tried. I hope you like it. Its my first mod, and will be my last. I\'m well aware not many players, like to chose High Elf as their character, but I\'m one of the rare ones who do. Haha 

(the primary picture is the same as the left one, i just added facial hair and change the color of the eyes. Nothing is changed of its core facial features.) 

Also sorry for my poor English, im from Russia.
